{
  "stem": "1568.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then I was left only with my brother and myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My brother was very sick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He broke out in-- first of all, he lost all his weight.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was just skin and bones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] broke out in terrible boils on his body.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was no cure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was no hospital.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was nothing that was involved.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we just existed on a daily basis like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And this was till about end of '43, I think, around December, where we were sent out-- Blizyn was closed out and we were sent out to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- myself and my brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went by train to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A train to-- to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the first thing you remember is my tattoo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My name went away and my tattoo became 1840.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- my name disappeared and I was become B1840.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] again, I guess, it is for some reason a lark.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In [SIGHS] Auschwitz, they put me into the kitchen to peel potatoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was-- by being the kitchen, I had enough food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I tried-- the only food I could bring out was raw potatoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would bring some out and give it to my brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But how-- you eat raw potatoes in the condition that his, it was even worse to help him out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this is the basic life, again, in-- in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In Auschwitz, you are only three months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Stop right there one second.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
